{"tid":2324424,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人返工屙屎都有bio clock?","createTime":"2020-12-14T02:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T18:06:28.000Z","uid":40930,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57cdb894b0f4a29a584dc26011322b130210a38e","tid":2324424,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:34:34.000Z","msg":"開會都有時間表，更何況係屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前成日都會係某段時間特別急屎，一支箭飛入廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到第日終於冇咗呢個情況後，慢慢就不自覺地變成咗習慣，好似返工打卡咁，夠鐘就來去如風<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好驚有一日身體習慣咗就返唔到轉頭，如果廁所阿姐個日突襲清潔，我咪最後係門口噴屎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62dd1955cc2015629df11d10062eeadb599e1a3f","tid":2324424,"uid":82752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"食完個早餐就急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cadd28da2a43e31690ea8b44b2e0015d7a7d1c","tid":2324424,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"慣左係公司食完早餐冇耐就急屎. 一放假係屋企就冇得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e0c485a3c439d08977750e49a631829a100040","tid":2324424,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"一打開隻眼 就想屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f485bd5f1860b0c44a7cc769d455cd81ff21dd1f","tid":2324424,"uid":86158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63cadd28da2a43e31690ea8b44b2e0015d7a7d1c","tid":2324424,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"慣左係公司食完早餐冇耐就急屎. 一放假係屋企就冇得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime"